title: Bhad Bhabie's Dad Disgusted: "She was exploited. They planned it for her 18th birthday."

media:group.media:title: Bhad Bhabie's Dad Disgusted: "She was exploited. They planned it for her 18th birthday."
media:group.media:description:
What was supposed to be 15 minutes of fame, turned into a career for this viral sensation. But when you’re thrust into the spotlight as a child and every misstep you take is seen by millions, it’s hard to know who’s looking out for your best interest. Now this star is an adult and her sudden decision to enter a controversial field of work has people shocked—even her father has spoken up.
